news.title: CapitaLand to develop IT park in Hyderabad with Rs 450 crore investment
news.para: Chief Minister Revanth Reddy welcomed the investment decision and described it as a milestone in reinforcing Hyderabad's position as a leading business and technology hub.

news.title: Maharashtra to launch online tenant verification system by February-end
news.para: The rollout, initially delayed due to software updates, will connect the registration department's database with police stations across 44,000 villages.

news.title: Allahabad HC asks Noida authority to start registry of Meghdutam housing project
news.para: A division bench of Justices Manoj Kumar Gupta and Anish Kumar Gupta issued the interim order on Jan 15, responding to a petition filed by 19 residents.

news.title: Over 280 properties given notices for building violations in Gurugram's DLF phase 1
news.para: Earlier, a survey of 3,658 properties in DLF phase 1 revealed violations in 301 houses. According to the department, these violations pertain to unauthorised construction and misuse of residential spaces for commercial purposes.

news.title: Dharavi redevelopment begins with government approval for first phase of rehabilitation
news.para: With this key approval, the first phase of the rehabilitation project involving over a million people will begin on a 6.4-acre land parcel in central Mumbai’s Matunga west and this will have to be completed over the next seven years.

news.title: Chandigarh administration plans big-ticket infra, housing projects in FY25-26
news.para: Around 150 houses are planned under the police housing project in Dhanas, besides 200 general houses in Sectors 43 and 46.

news.title: SEIAA grants environmental clearance for Tidel parks in Madurai and Trichy
news.para: The Madurai Tidel park will come up near the Mattuthavani bus stand on a 9.97-acre site, with a built-up area of 5.67 lakh sqft.

news.title: Thane Metro route delayed, costs escalate by Rs 63 crore
news.para: The MMRDA is the executing agency for the 2.7km long metro route, which is part of the entire 56km Metro corridor linking CSMT to Mira Road in four phases.

news.title: Sanofi Healthcare India leases 2.7 lakh sq ft office space in Hyderabad
news.para: The lease, registered earlier this month, began on January 1 and it spans six floors of RMZ Spire-Tower 110 in Hitech City, a hub for technology and business enterprises.

news.title: NCLT directs liquidation of Tulip Hotels as it fails to get bidder within prescribed timeline
news.para: On May 16, 2023, the NCLT had directed the initiation of a Corporate Insolvency Resolution Process (CIRP) against Tulip Hotels over a plea filed by Yes Bank, claiming a default of Rs 900 crore for two corporate guarantees issued by it.

news.title: Bengaluru civic body reaches 83% of its property tax target
news.para: By this time in 2023, BBMP had only collected Rs 3,480 crore, while current collection stands at Rs 4,370 crore. Weekly tax collection stands at Rs 10-13 crore at present; Mahadevapura Zone collects Rs 1,169 crore, achieving 89% of its target

news.title: MahaRERA directs Honest Shelters to hand over flats to IIFL
news.para: ​MahaRERA chairman Manoj Saunik, in his order, also directed the official liquidator to hand over the possession of the flats in his custody to the promoter for completing the construction. Thereafter, the promoter was to hand over possession of the same to IIFL with an occupancy certificate.

news.title: Hrithik Roshan lease out his office space in Mumbai
news.para: The property is located in Lotus Corporate Park, a commercial project by Lotus Developers. Spread across 27.55 acres, this project is located in Goregaon, Mumbai.

news.title: State departments among top property tax defaulters, owe over Rs 93 crore to Nagpur civic body
news.para: NMC's property tax department data reveals that total property tax arrears reached a whopping Rs850.1 crore, with govt departments alone accounting for Rs83.74 crore.

news.title: For now, MMRCL puts on hold plan to lease South Mumbai land
news.para: MMRCL issued a request for proposal (RFP) for the development of the land on Oct 3, 2024. However, a public notice issued on Saturday announced its withdrawal.

news.title: PM distributes over 65 lakh property cards under SVAMITVA scheme
news.para: The Prime Minister remarked that five years ago, the SVAMITVA scheme was launched to ensure that the people residing in the rural areas receive their property cards.

news.title: Coimbatore-based construction firm to compensate consumer for halting work
news.para: In his submission to the commission, M Asan Maideen stated that he had entered into an agreement with Idayarpalayam-based KR Builders on January 30, 2023 to build a new house measuring 1,507sqft on his land at Narasimanacikanpalayam.

news.title: Pune: PMRDA razes 50 illegal structures in Hinjewadi
news.para: Additionally, owners of around 50 properties around Laxmi Chowk removed encroached structures on their own after a warning issued by PMRDA.

news.title: Bhubaneswar: SJTA to launch online platform for land settlements
news.para: Currently, individuals occupying temple lands submit manual applications to SJTA for property sale or transfer. This current process, operating under the govt's Uniform Policy-2003, is lengthy and creates difficulties for applicants.

news.title: Hubballi-Dharwad civic body launches e-aasthi tax mela
news.para: The HDMC aims to enhance its revenue collection while achieving complete implementation of the e-AASTHI system.
